A:/> C:
C:/> # ============================================================
C:/> 
C:/> # Rename-After-Delete Torture Test
C:/> 
C:/> # Tests that rename operates correctly when the directory has
C:/> 
C:/> # holes (unused entries) from prior deletions, and that deleted
C:/> 
C:/> # filenames become available for reuse via rename.
C:/> 
C:/> #
C:/> 
C:/> # Exercises:
C:/> 
C:/> #   - Rename with freed slots preceding the target entry
C:/> 
C:/> #   - Rename to the name of a previously deleted file
C:/> 
C:/> #   - New file creation reusing a freed slot, then rename
C:/> 
C:/> #   - Content integrity through multiple renames
C:/> 
C:/> # ============================================================
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 1: Create several files
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT ALPHA.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT BRAVO.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT CHARLIE.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT DELTA.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT ECHO.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> DIR
Directory Listing:
    15 SCOTT.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEY.TXT
    55 HELLOWORLD.APP
  1339 RANDDATA.APP
  2050 MULTIFILE.APP
  1238 SIZETEST.APP
  1108 MORE.APP
  1579 WC.APP
  1830 TAIL.APP
  1158 HEAD.APP
  1318 APPEND.APP
     4 ONE.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEYF.TXT
     6 THREE.TXT
 <DIR> MYDIR
    15 ALPHA.TXT
     4 SIX.TXT
     6 SEVEN.TXT
     6 EIGHT.TXT
    15 BRAVO.TXT
    15 CHARLIE.TXT
    15 DELTA.TXT
     7 TWELVE.TXT
    15 ECHO.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 2: Delete some files to create holes in the directory
C:/> 
C:/> RF BRAVO.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF DELTA.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> DIR
Directory Listing:
    15 SCOTT.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEY.TXT
    55 HELLOWORLD.APP
  1339 RANDDATA.APP
  2050 MULTIFILE.APP
  1238 SIZETEST.APP
  1108 MORE.APP
  1579 WC.APP
  1830 TAIL.APP
  1158 HEAD.APP
  1318 APPEND.APP
     4 ONE.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEYF.TXT
     6 THREE.TXT
 <DIR> MYDIR
    15 ALPHA.TXT
     4 SIX.TXT
     6 SEVEN.TXT
     6 EIGHT.TXT
    15 CHARLIE.TXT
     7 TWELVE.TXT
    15 ECHO.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 3: Rename a file that comes after the holes
C:/> 
C:/> # CHARLIE.TXT's entry is between the two freed slots
C:/> 
C:/> NF CHARLIE.TXT CHARLIE2.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> # Verify rename worked and content is intact
C:/> 
C:/> LF CHARLIE2.TXT
scott was here
C:/> 
C:/> DIR
Directory Listing:
    15 SCOTT.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEY.TXT
    55 HELLOWORLD.APP
  1339 RANDDATA.APP
  2050 MULTIFILE.APP
  1238 SIZETEST.APP
  1108 MORE.APP
  1579 WC.APP
  1830 TAIL.APP
  1158 HEAD.APP
  1318 APPEND.APP
     4 ONE.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEYF.TXT
     6 THREE.TXT
 <DIR> MYDIR
    15 ALPHA.TXT
     4 SIX.TXT
     6 SEVEN.TXT
     6 EIGHT.TXT
    15 CHARLIE2.TXT
     7 TWELVE.TXT
    15 ECHO.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 4: Rename a file to the name of a deleted file
C:/> 
C:/> # BRAVO.TXT was deleted — that name should be reusable
C:/> 
C:/> NF ECHO.TXT BRAVO.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> LF BRAVO.TXT
scott was here
C:/> 
C:/> DIR
Directory Listing:
    15 SCOTT.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEY.TXT
    55 HELLOWORLD.APP
  1339 RANDDATA.APP
  2050 MULTIFILE.APP
  1238 SIZETEST.APP
  1108 MORE.APP
  1579 WC.APP
  1830 TAIL.APP
  1158 HEAD.APP
  1318 APPEND.APP
     4 ONE.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEYF.TXT
     6 THREE.TXT
 <DIR> MYDIR
    15 ALPHA.TXT
     4 SIX.TXT
     6 SEVEN.TXT
     6 EIGHT.TXT
    15 CHARLIE2.TXT
     7 TWELVE.TXT
    15 BRAVO.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 5: Create a new file that reuses a freed directory slot
C:/> 
C:/> # then rename it
C:/> 
C:/> CF SCOTT.TXT FOXTROT.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> NF FOXTROT.TXT GOLF.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> LF GOLF.TXT
scott was here
C:/> 
C:/> DIR
Directory Listing:
    15 SCOTT.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEY.TXT
    55 HELLOWORLD.APP
  1339 RANDDATA.APP
  2050 MULTIFILE.APP
  1238 SIZETEST.APP
  1108 MORE.APP
  1579 WC.APP
  1830 TAIL.APP
  1158 HEAD.APP
  1318 APPEND.APP
     4 ONE.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEYF.TXT
     6 THREE.TXT
 <DIR> MYDIR
    15 ALPHA.TXT
     4 SIX.TXT
     6 SEVEN.TXT
     6 EIGHT.TXT
    15 GOLF.TXT
    15 CHARLIE2.TXT
     7 TWELVE.TXT
    15 BRAVO.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 6: Chain of renames — rename the same file multiple times
C:/> 
C:/> NF ALPHA.TXT HOTEL.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> NF HOTEL.TXT INDIA.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> NF INDIA.TXT JULIET.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> LF JULIET.TXT
scott was here
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 7: Verify rename to existing name fails gracefully
C:/> 
C:/> # BRAVO.TXT exists; renaming CHARLIE2.TXT to BRAVO.TXT should fail
C:/> 
C:/> NF CHARLIE2.TXT BRAVO.TXT
Error: Already exists.
C:/> 
C:/> # Step 8: Clean up
C:/> 
C:/> RF JULIET.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF BRAVO.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF CHARLIE2.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> RF GOLF.TXT
C:/> 
C:/> # Verify filesystem is clean
C:/> 
C:/> DIR
Directory Listing:
    15 SCOTT.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEY.TXT
    55 HELLOWORLD.APP
  1339 RANDDATA.APP
  2050 MULTIFILE.APP
  1238 SIZETEST.APP
  1108 MORE.APP
  1579 WC.APP
  1830 TAIL.APP
  1158 HEAD.APP
  1318 APPEND.APP
     4 ONE.TXT
 21303 ODYSSEYF.TXT
     6 THREE.TXT
 <DIR> MYDIR
     4 SIX.TXT
     6 SEVEN.TXT
     6 EIGHT.TXT
     7 TWELVE.TXT
